Data Lakes 
Why
- data exploration
- advanced analytics, ML, graphs etc.

Effects of big data
- low costs
- ETL offloading
- dimensional modeling
- low cost of storage 
- Schema on read 
- Hive & spark - makes it easy to work with a file store.
spark.read.csv("xx.csv", inferschema=true)
- Reads data from diff formats (binary such as Avro, parquet (columnar)), gzip

- R/W from diff sources, S3, HDFS etc
-R/W from diff db
-

Data Lake options on AWS

Storage = HDFS or S3
Processing = Spark or serverless
AWS = EMR, Athena
